_json.description: Faux Window adds a sense of intrigue to your outdoor space with the illusion of having a window leading to another Garden entirely. Overall size approx : 70 diameter x 2(D) cm./ Mirror/Glass part: 60 diameter cm. A beautiful round wall mirror made from wood with a classic, vintage inspired window design. This item comes with a distressed White painted finish. For a variety of rooms that would fit into Vintage, Modern, Shabby Chic or Rustic inspired interiors. 2 hooks on reverse for hanging pleas
